%% Diagram: RSC streaming with parallel fetches and progressive Suspense flush
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant SR as Server Renderer
    participant DB as Database / API
    participant Cache as Per-request fetch cache

    B->>SR: GET /dashboard
    SR->>SR: render Page (RSC)
    par Parallel server fetches
        SR->>Cache: fetch(/users/me)
        Cache->>DB: query
        DB-->>Cache: user
        Cache-->>SR: user (memoised)
    and
        SR->>Cache: fetch(/orders, suspended)
        Cache->>DB: query (slow)
    and
        SR->>Cache: fetch(/feed, suspended)
        Cache->>DB: query (slow)
    end

    SR-->>B: chunk 1 (HTML shell + header + user)
    Note over B: TTFB / first paint

    DB-->>Cache: orders ready
    Cache-->>SR: orders
    SR-->>B: chunk 2 (Suspense reveal: orders)

    DB-->>Cache: feed ready
    Cache-->>SR: feed
    SR-->>B: chunk 3 (Suspense reveal: feed)
    SR-->>B: closing chunk
